      "comment": "CYCLONE MICK (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.55) in a Grade 6 at this track. Worth another chance. CANYA SHOTFIRE (4) pinged the lids from out wide but run ended and faded out of it late when 6th at Q Parklands in Grade 6 company. Should be about the money. SIRIUS MELITA (7) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at this track over 390m behind Boom Two Down (22.93) in a Grade 6. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. HARA'S BARRY (2) showed plenty of dash to record a debut win. Big chance on that form.",
